Package jpa.entities

Class Concert

java.lang.Object
jpa.entities.BaseEntity
jpa.entities.Concert
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class Concert extends BaseEntity
Concert aggregate created by an organizer and optionally validated by an admin.

New concerts start in PENDING_VALIDATION status and become publicly visible when promoted to PUBLISHED.
